          "description": "Per-client packet-loss percentages (attributes downstream.loss_percent / upstream.loss_percent / total.loss_percent), averaged across clients per sample interval.\n\nSchema note: OTel attributes land as Loki structured metadata (dot -> underscore, e.g. event.name -> event_name), filtered via a pipeline label filter after the selector - no logfmt/json parser stage - e.g. `{service_name=~\"...\"} | event_name=\"meraki.org.webhook.delivery\"`. LIVE-VERIFIED for meraki.org.webhook.delivery (flowing today); the equivalent field names for the two wireless-client events are ASSUMED by the same dot->underscore convention since zero records exist yet (blocked on #637) - re-verify once #637 lands.",
          "id": 5,
          "links": [],
